        </div>
        <div class="annotationText">
          <p>I have not yet seen the reMarkable tablet an action, though the website does make it look like a very different and potentially useful tool.</p>
<p>As Kevin mentioned, I've gone back and forth on this. However, I find that – at least in schools – if we don't name something clearly and explicitly then it will not get taught. That's why I still use the term "digital writing," though in many ways I completely agree that it feels out-of-place in everyday conversations.</p>
