        <span title="suffix" class="quoteSuffix"> – changes the practice of educa</span>
      
        </div>
        <div class="annotationText">
          <p>General openness is something we should be considering in OER. Is it possible to be too open? What are the extremes of OER and open? What controls or safeguards would protect from either extreme?</p>
