        <span title="quote" class="quoteExact"></span>
        <span title="suffix" class="quoteSuffix"></span>
      
        </div>
        <div class="annotationText">
          <p>I think the greatest problem with open are barriers of access. In both their technical use, which often rely on specialized discourses and interfaces, but more importantly in historical race and class based inequities. </p>
        </div>
        <div is="annotation-tags-editor" state="viewing" class="annotationTags" user-can-edit="false" tags="%5B%22%23openpedagogy%22%5D"><div class="annotationTag"><a target="_tag" href="https://jonudell.info/h/facet/?tag=#openpedagogy">#openpedagogy</a></div></div>
