        <div class="annotationText">
          <p>I think this is a great way to describe a teacher's role to students....that they are their tour guides.  A visual could even be created to explain both student and teacher roles as well as the expectations for all.  This approach could be used at all grades levels and might possible act as a "hook" to engage students as we've been discussing.  </p>
