        <div class="annotationText">
          <p>It is usually explicitly taught and often through games or activities that focus on a skill continuum. You:</p>
<ul>
<li>You identify beginning and ending sounds in words. Often starting with names.</li>
<li>You categorize sounds</li>
<li>You substitute sounds. (cat replaced with /b/)</li>
<li>You blend sounds</li>
<li>You segment sounds.</li>
